OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FTwo of the men hoping to oust Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer as Prime Minister have been
OL,8,Fcaught up in a debate over whether
OL,9,FLabour should seek to take Britain
OL,10,Fback into the European Union.
OL,12,FWes Streeting, the former health
OL,13,Fsecretary, on Saturday set out his
OL,14,Fdesire for a "new special
OL,15,Frelationship" with the EU, and to
OL,16,Feventually rejoin the trade bloc.
OL,26,@vD@NOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
