CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778983452
OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FAndy Burnham, the mayor of Greater
OL,7,FManchester, was meanwhile probed over
OL,8,Fhis support for returning to the EU as
OL,9,Fhe seeks to stand in a Brexit-voting,
OL,10,FReform UK-facing parliamentary
OL,11,Fconstituency.
OL,13,FJostling over Labour's future
OL,14,Fdirection on Europe began as the party
OL,15,Fdebates how to move on from its
OL,16,Fbruising election defeats last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778983452
OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FSpeaking at the Progress think tank's
OL,7,Fconference in central London on
OL,8,FSaturday, Mr Streeting described
OL,9,FBrexit as a "catastrophic mistake",
OL,10,Fand broke the ice on a topic which
OL,11,FLabour has long avoided revisiting.
OL,13,FThe British people see that "we must
OL,14,Fclub together" with near neighbours on
OL,15,Fthe continent "to rebuild our economy
OL,16,Fand trade, and improve our defence
OL,17,Fagainst the shared threats from
OL,18,FRussian aggression and America First",
OL,19,Fhe added.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@bO]uD@]OUvD@NO]wD@OOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
