OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778983452
OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FRounding off his proposal, Mr
OL,7,FStreeting said: "The biggest economic
OL,8,Fopportunity we have is on our doorstep.
OL,10,F"We need a new special relationship
OL,11,Fwith the EU, because Britain's future
OL,12,Flies with Europe ` and one day back in
OL,13,Fthe European Union."
OL,26,@oD@QOUrD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
