OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FThe policy offer could also be read as
OL,7,Fa direct challenge to Mr Burnham, who
OL,8,Fhas previously expressed support for
OL,9,Frejoining the EU, but may wish to
OL,10,Favoid directly speaking about the
OL,11,Fissue as he bids to become Labour's
OL,12,Fcandidate in the upcoming Makerfield
OL,13,Fby-election.
OL,15,FThe constituency on the edge of
OL,16,FGreater Manchester was a Brexit-voting
OL,17,Farea in the referendum held nearly 10
OL,18,Fyears ago on June 23 2016.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
