PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778983452
OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FTory chairman Kevin Hollinrake said:
OL,7,F"Whilst Labour relitigate Brexit,
OL,8,FBritain is not being governed.
OL,10,F"This is yet another distraction from
OL,11,Fthe day job at a time when families
OL,12,Fand businesses want the Government
OL,13,Ffocused on the cost of living, the
OL,14,Feconomy, public services and Britain's
OL,15,Fdefence."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
