OL,3,CLabour leadership rivals caught up in
OL,4,Cdebate over EU ties
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,7,Fmeanwhile said Mr Streeting must
OL,8,F"offer something more than the same
OL,9,Ffailed red lines as Keir Starmer" if
OL,10,Fhe is to succeed the Prime Minister,
OL,11,Fand called for negotiations on a
OL,12,Fcustoms union with the EU to be opened.
OL,14,FSir Keir has indicated he wants to see
OL,15,Fmuch closer ties with Europe,
OL,16,Fbeginning with a youth mobility deal
OL,17,Fset to be finalised this summer.
OL,19,FHe also did not rule out Labour
OL,20,Fseeking even closer ties in a future
OL,21,Felection manifesto.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@aO]
